HotelDescription#The hotel is located on Pusa Lane, opposite Metro Pillar no. 88 in Karol Bagh, Asia's biggest shopping arcade. This hotel is located close to Connaught Place, Pragati Maidan, and Karol Bagh metro station. It is located approximately 22 km away from the international airport and 6 km from New Delhi railway station.

This is a modernly decorated hotel mainly designed for modern day business and leisure travellers. The architecture is complemented by the smart furnishings and high standard of comfortable interiors. The hotel has air conditioning and welcomes guests in the lobby, which offers a 24-hour reception, a hotel safe and currency exchange facilities. There is a newspaper stand and wireless Internet access. Guests can dine in the restaurant and enjoy a drink at the coffee shop. The hotel also provides room and laundry services as well as a car park for those arriving by car. An on-call doctor service is offered by the hotel.

The hotel provides luxuriously appointed rooms and suites with smartly crafted curtains, modern furniture and Italian flooring. All rooms are comfortable and spacious and come en suite with a shower and bath. Guests can enjoy a good night's rest on their double bed. Rooms provide all modern amenities such as air conditioning, an LCD TV, telephone, Internet access, tea and coffee making facilities and a safe. A fridge, individually regulated heating and a balcony or terrace are standard features of all accommodation.
